      "title": "Negotiate an enforceable community-benefits agreement (CBA)",
      "detail": "In a top-quartile cumulative-burden tract, a CBA with independent monitoring (local hiring, utility-bill relief, health investments) is the credible floor for community legitimacy — not a voluntary donation program.",
