      "pillar": "burden",
      "title": "Eliminate on-site combustion backup where feasible",
      "detail": "Diesel/gas backup fleets concentrate exactly the pollutants (diesel PM, NOx) that drive the tract's existing burden. BESS backup, Tier 4 Final engines with runtime caps, and grid-interactive UPS remove the largest local air-quality delta.",
